## Measurements

Select the tab below to view measurement options for each taxonomic group.

{% tabs %}
{% tabitem label="Mammals" %}

- `Total length (mm)`: the total length of the specimen including from to tip of the nose to the tip of the tail.
- `Tail length (mm)`: the length of the tail from the base to the tip.
- `Head and body length (mm)`: Auto calculated from the `Total length (mm) - Tail length (mm)`.
- `Tail/HB length` percentage: Auto calculated from the `Tail length (mm) / Head and body length (mm)`.
- `Hind foot length (mm)`: the length of the hind foot from the base to the tip of the claw.

{% /tabitem %}
